name: Ready To Go Banner
description:
Make your blog awesome with a custom banner.
First, I make a mood board, inspired by your blog/shop to discover the true you. It will help to make  the perfect banner. A quick fix to stand out from the crowd!

What you get:
- a mood board reflecting you are, what your blog/shop is about.
- a JPG at the your needed size.
- 1 revision.
